	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Takes you to your designated &quot;home&quot; point--essentially where you would show up if you died.  In order to change that point, you will need the 'Bind Affinity' spell--or at least to have someone else Bind you to a new &quot;home&quot; point.  This will bind you to the home point for that zone.  Not the speediest or cheapest spell to cast--but nice when your hit points are depleted and you just want to go home and fish for awhile.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#D6D1BE">	
		
	
