				Druids: This, used with Bind Affinity can be very useful. Once you get teleport starting at 19, 24, and 29, it stops being a major concern where you are bound. Even if you die you can teleport to within a few zones of your body, and just SoW and hoof it over. Plus you can stay bound in OoT, or some other out of the way place even if you aren't fighting there, and still get back quickly with Gate instead of waitin fur the boat.<BR>
